{
  "_meta": {
    "description": "12 category pairs from Wickens (1970) and colleagues, extracted from Mewhort, Shabahang & Franklin (2018, Psychon Bull Rev) Appendix. Each pair was used in the classic Release from PI paradigm. RPI values = observed release size (0=none, 1=full).",
    "paper": "Mewhort, Shabahang & Franklin (2018). Release from PI: An analysis and a model. Psychonomic Bulletin & Review, 25, 932-950.",
    "usage": "For each pair: cat_a = induction category, cat_b = release category. Recall mode: 3 trials of cat_a words, then 1 trial of cat_b (experimental) or cat_a (control). Rating mode: sequential single-word rating interleaving both categories."
  },
